content:
Welcome to #australia/primary-care.

Description: Australian Primary Care Data Quality working groups

Just in case anyone is new, there's more information about work in this space at https://confluence.csiro.au/display/primarecaredata. We're also working towards an IG for practice-to-practice primary care record transfer, although its still very early days for us

And a reminder that the model we were looking at is found at http://clinfhir.com/csiroProject.html . Click the 'common model' link to view the model. Remember to log in (the icon in the upper right) to make new comments (or add notes to older ones). I'll post notifications here when I update the tooling (for those interested - entirely optional of course!)
